  <note>
    <title>4FTI&apos;s list for a reset of TRC</title>
    <created>19700107T055220Z</created>
    <updated>20141223T082031Z</updated>
    <tag>Reset</tag>
    <tag>TRC</tag>
    <note-attributes>
      <author>sslooten</author>
    </note-attributes>
    <content>
      <![CDATA[<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?>
<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd"><en-note style="word-wrap: break-word; -webkit-nbsp-mode: space; -webkit-line-break: after-white-space;">

	
	
	<div>

		
		
		<div><span style="font-size: 14px;">Final version</span></div>

		
		
		<div><span style="font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></div>

		
		
		<div>

			
			
			<div style="font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;">

				
				
				<div>

					
					
					<div>

						
						
						<p><span lang="EN-US"><font color="#00007F">This is the minimal indispensable list from 4FTI. We are willing to discuss adding things to this list. Removing anything from this list is not open to discussion</font></span></p>

					
					
					</div>

					
					
					<div>

						
						
						<ul>

							
							
							<li><font color="#00007F">Immediate and unconditional handover of</font>

								
								
								<ul>

									
									
									<li><font color="#00007F">Domain registration un/pw (all domains, incl. <a href="http://railo.io">railo.io</a>)</font></li>

									
									
									<li><font color="#00007F">Github master un/pw</font></li>

									
									
									<li><font color="#00007F">Freshdesk, Mailchimp and all other systems master un/pw</font></li>

									
									
									<li><font color="#00007F">Mura un/pw for all sites</font></li>

									
									
									<li><font color="#00007F">Sources for installers</font></li>

									
									
									<li><font color="#00007F">All testcases</font></li>

									
									
									<li><font color="#00007F">All (unpublished) sources for R5 and other</font></li>

									
									
									<li><font color="#00007F">All sources, scripts &amp; other files not in git</font></li>

									
									
									<li><font color="#00007F">Master files for logo’s</font></li>

									
									
									<li><font color="#00007F">Training materials (slides, code etc)</font></li>

									
									
									<li><font color="#00007F">Master files for published books under RT brand</font></li>

									
									
									<li><font color="#00007F">.. All that is not mentioned here, but is related to the IP</font></li>

								
								
								</ul>

							
							
							</li>

						
						
						</ul>

					
					
					</div>

					
					
					<div>

						
						
						<ul>

							
							
							<li><font color="#00007F">All IP is owned by TRC</font></li>

							
							
							<li><font color="#00007F">Calle is MD</font></li>

							
							
							<li><font color="#00007F">MD is installed by Shareholders</font></li>

							
							
							<li><font color="#00007F"><span lang="EN-US">MD reports to the Board (or shareholders, </span><span lang="EN-US">when </span><span lang="EN-US">no Board exists (see below))</span></font></li>

							
							
							<li><font color="#00007F">ALL financial commitments to an amount of 5K (with a total of 20K per month) to be approved by MD</font></li>

							
							
							<li><font color="#00007F">ALL financial commitments to an amount of 20K (with a total of 40K per month) to be approved by Board</font></li>

							
							
							<li><font color="#00007F">ALL other financial commitments to be approved by Shareholders </font></li>

							
							
							<li><font color="#00007F">MD to sign 1-year contract with TRC with renewal option (subject to Shareholder approval)</font></li>

							
							
							<li><font color="#00007F">Clearly defined list with topics that MD can not decide on and that should be handled by Board</font></li>

							
							
							<li><font color="#00007F">Remuneration for MD is EUR. 5K per month, commencing on Jan 1st (as TRC needs to create financial buffer)</font></li>

						
						
						</ul>

					
					
					</div>

				
				
				</div>

				
				
				<div>

					
					
					<ul>

						
						
						<li><font color="#00007F"><span lang="EN-US">4FTI list of amendments to existing shareholder</span><span lang="EN-US"> agreement:</span></font>

							
							
							<ul>

								
								
								<li><font color="#00007F">Deadlock to be removed from agreements</font></li>

								
								
								<li><font color="#00007F">Shareholders decide by majority of votes, except articles in the already present list that requires 85% of the votes</font></li>

								
								
								<li><font color="#00007F">Repurchase right only possible when TRC fails for financial reasons (bankrupt)</font></li>

								
								
								<li><font color="#00007F">Repurchase price is valued against paid dividend (price = 45K + any paid dividends onder the 15% rule in the agreements) </font></li>

							
							
							</ul>

						
						
						</li>

					
					
					</ul>

				
				
				</div>

				
				
				<div>

					
					
					<div>

						
						
						<ul>

							
							
							<li><span lang="EN-US"><font color="#00007F">If BR and GMBH insist on a board and board not dissolved, then Board will consist of 4 members:</font></span>

								
								
								<ul>

									
									
									<li><font color="#00007F">1 for 4F with 3 votes (based on share %)</font></li>

									
									
									<li><font color="#00007F">1 for BR with 1 vote (based on share %)</font></li>

									
									
									<li><font color="#00007F">1 for RT with 2 votes (based on share %)</font></li>

									
									
									<li><font color="#00007F">MD with 1 vote, who also is the chairman of the Board, he has swing vote in case of tie.</font></li>

									
									
									<li><font color="#00007F">Board decides with majority of votes</font></li>

									
									
									<li><font color="#00007F">ALL Board members to be approved by shareholders (also the current members)</font></li>

									
									
									<li><font color="#00007F">Board &amp; all Board members enter into a 1 year agreement with renewal option</font></li>

								
								
								</ul>

								
								
								<div>

									
									
									<ul>

										
										
										<li><font color="#00007F">Board to meet with pre-approved agenda &amp; resolutions</font></li>

										
										
										<li><font color="#00007F">Board will NOT handle day-to-day operations</font></li>

									
									
									</ul>

									
									
									<ul>

										
										
